➜【星连文学社】广东诗人小隐：青玉案.花间茶话
http://www.sohu.com/a/411263178_100115135	40487
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200803/9caa5d47eb404c9287e318d6b12379d5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;"></span>青玉案.花间茶话</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/小隐</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小湖园里幽深处，翠绿色，和风舞。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">日暮歌声谁与诉，人间难住，花间欲住。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">闲话聊今古。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">懒人独自逍遥去，隐尘事，修花圃。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">犹记梦中强作赋，词中成句，茶中得句。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一夜听风雨。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200803/d1759d799e89433ca8fc7cd822937016.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
