<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《七月的雨》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/青衣小生</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">风，轻敲门窗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一场雨在七月来临</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">与你相遇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">抚慰一颗孤独的心</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">留下深刻的记忆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七月的雨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>绿叶流水间停留禅意</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>超脱了尘世间的爱与恨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那些被遗忘的畏惧与颓废</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>去寻找歇底里的呐喊</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>依然存在渴望</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>却封闭在自由的空间里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">七月的雨，淅淅沥沥</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">像在讲述故事的点滴</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">远处的曼陀罗花</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">被一份份温暖的爱分享</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
